Package jeco.core.benchmarks

Class TSP

java.lang.Object
jeco.core.problem.Problem<Variable<Integer>>
jeco.core.benchmarks.TSP
public class TSP extends Problem<Variable<Integer>>
Traveling Salesman Problem. The TSP is a classic optimization problem. The goal is to find the shortest possible route that visits each city exactly once and returns to the origin city. The TSP is a NP-hard problem. The number of possible solutions is n! (n factorial). The TSP is a minimization problem. The fitness of a solution is the total distance of the route.
